Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.04,0:23:27.67,edj,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,250)\frz-90\pos(20,180)\blur1}数え切れぬ 嵐を越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:33.14,edj,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,250)\frz-90\pos(20,180)\blur1}あなたの闇 裂くヒカリになる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.34,0:23:38.35,edj,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,250)\frz-90\pos(20,180)\blur1}もう 迷わない ともに生きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.52,0:23:43.81,edj,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,250)\frz-90\pos(20,180)\blur1}誓う夢が どんな無謀であっても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.02,0:23:53.61,edj,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,250)\frz-90\pos(20,180)\blur1}おぼえていて 信じられる場所は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.82,0:23:57.37,edj,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,250)\frz-90\pos(20,180)\blur1}ここにあると
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.33,0:22:44.96,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,250)\frz-90\pos(620,180)\blur1}只是  在时代的正当中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.67,0:22:50.47,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,250)\frz-90\pos(620,180)\blur1}无助  彷徨之时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.01,0:22:55.97,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,250)\frz-90\pos(620,180)\blur1}一直尽可能的寻找着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.35,0:23:00.02,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,250)\frz-90\pos(620,180)\blur1}可以拉住我的手的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:05.48,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,250)\frz-90\pos(620,180)\blur1}不断受伤  不断微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.98,0:23:10.82,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,250)\frz-90\pos(620,180)\blur1}心底  满是泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.11,0:23:16.29,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,250)\frz-90\pos(620,180)\blur1}能够听到那求救的声音的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.66,0:23:22.12,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,250)\frz-90\pos(620,180)\blur1}只有被准许之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.04,0:23:27.67,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,250)\frz-90\pos(620,180)\blur1}历经无数风霜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:33.14,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,250)\frz-90\pos(620,180)\blur1}只为成为斩断你心中幽暗的阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.34,0:23:38.35,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,250)\frz-90\pos(620,180)\blur1}已经不再踌躇  想和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.52,0:23:43.81,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,250)\frz-90\pos(620,180)\blur1}就算与你誓约是南柯一梦  不加思虑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.02,0:23:53.61,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,250)\frz-90\pos(620,180)\blur1}但请你记住  可以相信的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.82,0:23:57.37,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,250)\frz-90\pos(620,180)\blur1}只有这里
